description:
The magic of Capilene is its ability to wick moisture and dry fast. With a smooth outer surface, the double-knit fabric of slides under your top layers. A brushed-grid pattern on the back holds warmth near your skin. Not too heavy, not too light, this mid-weight option takes you from alpine snowfields to early season campsites.Made of gridded recycled polyester double-knit.HeiQ® Fresh Tech durable odour treatment.Riib-knit collar with internal neck tape for comfort.Raglan shoulder seams allow freedom of movement.Underarm gusset for range of motion.Hidden elastic thumb loops.

